description:
In this Minecraft episode we work towards getting some basic gear and getting settled, but it doesn't take long before we find lots of very cool things along the way. This time us MindCrackers are going to be at war with each other, pillaging and plundering to our hearts content. Time will tell to see how this develops.

MindCrack FTB is a modded Minecraft server Guude has setup for the MindCrackers. It is a private (whitelisted) server. We are currently not accepting applications.

FTB: http://feed-the-beast.com/
MindCrack: http://www.youtube.com/user/MindCrackNetwork
